title: It's a Zombie Apocalypse
itunes:title: It's a Zombie Apocalypse
description:
The Coronavirus is waking people up. Right now, more people than ever are starting to realize that they have been living most of their lives in a low grade zombie state. They are alive but they're not really living. In this episode, I am going to teach you how to wake up and make sure you get the most out of this quarantine.

Follow me on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/robdialjr/
